    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1043">
<l>tolvaravun tōluṅ keṭukkun tokaiyāka</l>
<l>nalkura veṉṉu nacai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Hankering poverty destroys at once the greatness of (one's) ancient descent and (the dignity of one's) speech.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
